[ Upstream commit 77907a068717fbefb25faf01fecca553aca6ccaa ]

jhash_1word accepts host endian inputs while rs_bound_port is a be16
value (sockaddr_in6.sin6_port). Use ntohs() for consistency.

Flagged by Sparse.

